OL,3,CPregnant mums given money incentive
OL,4,Cfrom NHS to help stop smoking
OL,6,FNew and expectant mothers spoke to ITV
OL,7,FGranada Reports correspondent Andy
OL,8,FBonner about the scheme which is
OL,9,Fhelping them to stop smoking
OL,11,FA scheme to stop pregnant women
OL,12,Fsmoking is helping more new mums than
OL,13,Fever - after the NHS began paying some
OL,14,Fto encourage them to quit.
OL,16,FMums-to-be who pass regular check-ups
OL,17,Fcan earn #20 a month for the duration
OL,18,Fof their pregnancy, which the health
OL,19,Fservice says saves it money in the
OL,20,Flong run.
