OL,3,CPregnant mums given money incentive
OL,4,Cfrom NHS to help stop smoking
OL,6,FExpectant women are offered less
OL,7,Fharmful vapes or nicotine replacement
OL,8,Ftherapy to help them quit alongside
OL,9,Fregular support either at home or in
OL,10,Fthe community.
OL,12,F"It's a hard habit to break,"
OL,13,Fexpectant mother Marina Durbano said.
OL,14,F"When you have the support of people
OL,15,Fthat understand what you're going
OL,16,Fthrough, it doesn't feel like a box
OL,17,Fticking appointment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
