OL,3,CPregnant mums given money incentive
OL,4,Cfrom NHS to help stop smoking
OL,6,F"And then she leaves a little message
OL,7,Fsaying, 'you're a star, you're doing
OL,8,Famazing', and when you're pregnant,
OL,9,Ftrust me, that counts every little bit.
OL,11,F"And then you have the vouchers at the
OL,12,Fend of that, which are great."
OL,14,FNew mum Gemma Carrigher, who has a
OL,15,Fnine-month-old named George, says the
OL,16,Fsupport makes all the difference.
OL,18,F"It just helps a little bit more
OL,19,Fhaving someone to support you to make
OL,20,Fsure that you're doing it as well,"
OL,21,Fshe said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
