OL,6,F"Because it's not just for you doing
OL,7,Fit for, you do it for your baby as
OL,8,Fwell. So it makes a huge difference,
OL,9,Fyou're becoming a non smoker to have a
OL,10,Fnon smoking baby."
OL,12,FExpectant mother Marina Durbano says
OL,13,Fthe support of others is what helps
OL,14,Fwhen it comes to giving up smoking
OL,16,FAlysha Lepinnet, new mum to son Tarik,
OL,17,Fsuccessfully used the scheme to stop
OL,18,Fher smoking habit. She added: "You got
OL,19,F#20 every month if you passed not
OL,20,Fsmoking.
