OL,6,F"It just helped me out because I came
OL,7,Fout of work in April so I was able to
OL,8,Fbuy things for the baby."
OL,10,FShe says she is already feeling the
OL,11,Fbenefits both in terms of her health
OL,12,Fand financially.
OL,14,F"100% I feel better for it," she said.
OL,15,F"Obviously the money, not buying all
OL,16,Fthe buying the cigarettes, you're
OL,17,Fsaving, then obviously he's just
OL,18,Fgetting more money saved up for him so
OL,19,Fhe's got a better future."
