OL,3,CPregnant mums given money incentive
OL,4,Cfrom NHS to help stop smoking
OL,6,FThe scheme - part of a national
OL,7,Fprogramme launched 12 months ago - is
OL,8,Fbased on efforts in Greater Manchester
OL,9,Fwhere the proportion of women smoking
OL,10,Fat birth fell by 40%.
OL,12,FIt has led to more than 6,000
OL,13,Fadditional babies being born smoke-
OL,14,Ffree since 2018.
OL,16,FThe NHS says stopping smoking will
OL,17,Fhelp both mum and baby immediately,
OL,18,Fwith the effects will be long-lasting.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
