OL,3,CPregnant mums given money incentive
OL,4,Cfrom NHS to help stop smoking
OL,6,FIt said complications in pregnancy and
OL,7,Fbirth will be reduced, while babies
OL,8,Fare less likely to be born too early
OL,9,For under weight.
OL,11,FThere is also less chance of sudden
OL,12,Finfant death syndrome or cot death.
OL,14,FAlexa, who has worked on the scheme in
OL,15,FBolton for 18 months, said it is
OL,16,Fmaking a big difference by reducing
OL,17,Fthe number of poorly babies needing
OL,18,Fcare.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
