OL,6,F"Financially, think about those
OL,7,Fbabies," she said. "We have saved
OL,8,Fbabies lives that we've eliminated and
OL,9,Fremoved from going into neonatal unit
OL,10,Fand having that extra care born
OL,11,Fpremature.
OL,13,F"So yeah, financially, we're massively
OL,14,Fsaving the NHS."
OL,16,FProfessor Jamie Waterall, Deputy Chief
OL,17,FPublic Nurse for England, said schemes
OL,18,Flike this one are "highly effective".
